data.description: 3 bedroom 2 bath home with additional double-door FLEX room in the heart of SW Palm Bay. Vaulted ceilings, enormous family room that adjoins the dining area and the oversized kitchen with feature island! The primary bedroom has an extra-large walk-in closet, separate garden tub, shower, and twin lavatory sinks. The back yard starts with a 12' x 20' truss-covered porch and the sodded yard is enclosed by a 6 foot wood privacy fence.
